        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1413210124" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1231031560345186182">Achingly beautiful and deeply moving this is the closest any book has come to bring a tear to my eye, the friendship between the Langs and the Morgans was so strong and heart warming it has profoundly affected the way I look at life and that of my loved ones. Impeccably written by Stegner who I believe was in his late seventies at the time, this really is a timeless novel that would break even those who carry a heart of stone.</span>

          </span>
